data.description: Look at this nice-sized ranch style home located in Steele. Enjoy the quite small town atmosphere, just a short drive from the city of Bismarck. The Main Level of this home features 3 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, a galley kitchen that looks out onto the dining room. The living room has great natural light and is just the right size for entertaining guests. The lower level is ready to be customized to fit your needs featuring a nice size family rec/area, 2 more bedrooms, a bathroom, and a nice size laundry/storage area. There is also a 2 stall attached garage for your vehicles.  Don't wait call a Realtor today you will not be disappointed.
